title: Dawn French's holiday home is up for sale
text:
Dawn French at a press night earlier this month Credit: PA Comedian Dawn French's holiday home in Cornwall - boasting 15 bedrooms and panoramic harbour views - has come on the market for £725,000.
The Vicar Of Dibley star runs Clipper House in West Looe as a holiday let business. It is split into three guest houses which could mean a sizeable income for the buyer.
The property, which can be found on Rightmove, also features a large living area, bar and games room.
Clipper House is on the market for £725,000 Credit: SWNS It has a panoramic view of the harbour Credit: SWNS Who would live in a house like this? Credit: SWNS Last updated Tue 29 Sep 2015 Entertainment West Looe Dawn French Cornwall and Isles of Scilly
